OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning cloud clearing to leave
OL,6,Fanother dry and sunny day. The
OL,7,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Temperatures a little lower
OL,9,Fthan of late in the north as winds
OL,10,Fturn northerly, but feeling hot in the
OL,11,Fsouth.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMost seeing clear spells
OL,14,Fovernight with intermittent areas of
OL,15,Fcloud. Winds dropping out and staying
OL,16,Fmild overnight, but more comfortable
OL,17,Fthan recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,169,160,301,260,100,100
