OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA bright start, though cloud
OL,6,Fbuilding throughout the morning. This
OL,7,Fbringing the odd shower by the
OL,8,Fafternoon but some sunny spells still
OL,9,Fbreaking through. Temperatures
OL,10,Fdropping for all.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStaying
OL,13,Fdry into the second half of the
OL,14,Fweekend, with sunny spells by day and
OL,15,Fclear skies at night. Temperatures
OL,16,Ftrending a little nearer to average,
OL,17,Fbut still feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
